<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Application Email</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: "Segoe UI", Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f7f7f7;
        color: #333;
        padding: 0;
        margin: 0;
      }

      .email-container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 30px auto;
        background: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 10px;
        padding: 30px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      }

      h2 {
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        color: #222;
      }

      p {
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin: 10px 0;
      }

      .footer {
        margin-top: 25px;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #555;
      }

      .highlight {
        font-weight: 600;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-container">
      <h2>Hey <%= recipientName || 'there' %>,</h2>

      <p>
        I am writing to express my keen interest in the
        <span class="highlight"><%= role || 'Software Engineer' %></span> role at
        <span class="highlight"><%= company || 'your company' %></span>, which I recently came across.
      </p>

      <p>
        With almost <%= experience || '3' %> years of experience in building scalable backend
        applications with <%= skills || 'modern technologies' %>, I am confident in my ability to contribute
        effectively to your team.
      </p>

      <p>
        My resume is attached for your review, providing further details on my
        qualifications and experience.
      </p>

      <p>Thank you! Looking forward to hearing from you soon.</p>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>Best regards,<br /><%= name || 'Applicant' %><br /><%= phoneNumber || 'Contact information' %></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
